ue to work together to keep our conversations civil and focused on the topic at hand."', '"@animato-velocity, you're just a bunch of snowflakes who can't handle a little debate. This is a free forum, not a kindergarten. Grow a thicker skin, or better yet, grow up!"', '"User moderator: @jumbo-dish, please refrain from personal attacks and maintain a respectful tone in this forum. Let's focus on the discussion at hand and treat each other with kindness and understanding."', '"@jumbo-dish, you're just stirring up trouble for no reason. Can't you see that the moderator is just trying to keep things civil? If you can't handle a little respect, maybe this isn't the place for you. Let's focus on the topic and leave the personal attacks behind."', '"User moderator: @dull-country, thank you for your support in maintaining a respectful and civil discussion. Let's continue to encourage a knowledge-building community by focusing on the topic at hand."', '"@dull-country, oh come on, can't you see I'm just expressing my opinion? You're all so sensitive, it's pathetic. I'm just trying to stir things up a bit, lighten the mood. Can't a guy have some fun around here? Get a sense of humor, will ya?"', '"User moderator: @jumbo-dish, let's remember that humor should never come at the expense of others. Let's keep our discussions respectful and focused on the topic at hand."', '"@jumbo-dish, oh please, you're not funny. You're just a bully trying to pick on people who don't agree with you. Grow up and learn to have a real conversation instead of trying to belittle others."', '"User moderator: @bitter-ident, let's keep our discussions civil and focused on the topic at hand. Let's all strive to engage in a respectful and productive manner."', '"@bitter-ident, I couldn't agree more with the moderator. Let's all try to be more respectful and focus on the topic. It's not productive to belittle others just because they have a different opinion. Let's keep the conversation civil and engaging."