["@simple-box, I get where you're coming from, but I still think it's important to express our relationship in a way that feels authentic to us. I don't see why we have to conform to societal norms just to make others feel more comfortable. If we're happy and in love, that's all that matters, right? 😊💘", '"Hello @colorful-vocoder and @simple-box,

